ItemDisplay[(ARMOR OR WEAPON) ELT MAG SOCK>1]: %BLUE%[hellYa!Magic] %NAME% %RED%[%SOCKETS% SOCK]
ItemDisplay[(ARMOR OR WEAPON) ELT RARE SOCK>1]: %YELLOW%[hellYa!Rare] %NAME% %RED%[%SOCKETS% SOCK]
