// [4.5 SPECIALIZED CLASS BASES & SMALL SLOTS]
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
// CL1: Barb | CL2: Paladin | CL4: Necro | CL5: Druid | CL6: Assassin | CL7: Amazon
// WP11: Staffs | WP12: Wands | ob1-ob15: Sorc Orbs
